  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nAccording to https://quarkus.io/guides/datasource#datasource-tracing, the `quarkus.datasource.jdbc.tracing` property is not even mentioned in the docs (except in the config table) and requires the `io.opentracing.contrib.jdbc.TracingDriver` driver to be present in the classpath (I figured that out by reading the code). \r\n \r\n\r\n### Implementation ideas\r\n\r\nDeprecate the `quarkus.datasource.jdbc.tracing` configuration and remove in a future version",
